# Models Directory

Place your GGUF model files here.

## Recommended Models

### DASD-4B-Thinking
A 4B parameter cybersecurity-focused reasoning model.

**Download:**
- [Hugging Face - DASD-4B-Thinking-GGUF](https://huggingface.co/MaziyarPanahi/DASD-4B-Thinking-GGUF)

**Recommended quantization:**
- `DASD-4B-Thinking.Q4_K_M.gguf` (2.5GB) - Good balance
- `DASD-4B-Thinking.Q8_0.gguf` (4.0GB) - Higher quality

## Alternative Models

Any GGUF format model compatible with llama-cpp-python will work. Update `MODEL_PATH` in your `.env` file.

Popular options:
- Llama 3.1 (8B, 70B variants)
- Mistral 7B
- Phi-3
- Gemma 2